msgid "UI plugin to split off parts of an epub into a new book."
msgstr "將epub的拆分為新書的外掛。"

msgid "Title for each new book will be taken from the first included section in the Table of Contents above, which you can edit here first."
msgstr "每本新書的標題都將取自上述目錄中包含的第一個章節，您可以在此先編輯它。"

msgid "New Book per Section"
msgstr "每個章節一本書"

msgid "Make a new book for <i>each</i> of the sections selected above."
msgstr "所選部分的 <i>每個</i> 章節生成一本書."

msgid "New Book per N Sections"
msgstr "每N個章節一本書"

msgid "Make new books, each containing N sections from those selected above."
msgstr "製作新書，每本包含上面所選內容中的 N 個章節。"

msgid "N New Books"
msgstr "N本新書"

msgid "Make N new books by evenly dividing the sections selected above."
msgstr "透過均勻劃分上面選定的部分的章節數來製作 N 本新書。"

msgid "Basic"
msgstr "基礎設定"

msgid "Custom Columns"
msgstr "自定義欄目"

msgid "New Book Per"
msgstr "自動拆分"

msgid "Edit Metadata for New Book(s)"
msgstr "編輯新書籍的後設資料"

msgid "Show Edit Metadata Dialog after creating each new book entry, but <i>before</i> EPUB is created.<br>Allows for downloading metadata and ensures EPUB has updated metadata."
msgstr "在建立每個新書條目之後, 但在建立EPUB <i>之前</i> ，顯示“編輯後設資料”對話方塊。<br>允許下載後設資料，並確保EPUB具有更新的後設資料。"

msgid "Show 'Always Include' Checkboxes"
msgstr "顯示“始終包含”核取方塊"

msgid "If enabled, a checkbox will appear for each section."
msgstr "如果啟用，每個章節都會出現一個核取方塊。"

msgid "Checked sections will be included in <i>all</i> split books.<br>Default title will still be taken from the first <i>selected</i> section, and section order will remain as shown."
msgstr "選中的部分將包括在<i>all </i>拆分的書籍中。<br>預設標題仍將取自第一個<i>選定的</i>部分，並且部分順序將保持如圖所示。"

msgid "When making a new Epub, the metadata from the source book will be copied or not as you choose below."
msgstr "製作新的Epub時，源書中的後設資料將被複制或不被複制，如下所示。"

msgid "Title from First Included TOC"
msgstr "從首個內建目錄中獲取標題"

msgid "Copy Title from the the first Table of Contents entry included in the Split Epub.\nSupersedes Copy Title below."
msgstr "從Split Epub中包含的第一個目錄條目複製標題。取代下面的複製標題。"

msgid "Copy Title"
msgstr "複製書名"

msgid "Copy Title from the source Epub to the Split Epub.  Adds \"Split\" to the title."
msgstr "將書名從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。 新增 \"拆分\" 到書名中. "

msgid "Copy Authors"
msgstr "復製作者"

msgid "Copy Authors from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將作者從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Series"
msgstr "複製叢書"

msgid "Copy Series from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將叢書從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Cover"
msgstr "複製封面"

msgid "Copy Cover from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將封面從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Rating"
msgstr "複製評分"

msgid "Copy Rating from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將評分從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Tags"
msgstr "複製標籤"

msgid "Copy Tags from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將標籤從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Identifiers"
msgstr "複製書號"

msgid "Copy Identifiers from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將識別符號從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Date"
msgstr "複製建立日期"

msgid "Copy Date from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將建立日期從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Published Date"
msgstr "複製出版日期"

msgid "Copy Published Date from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將出版日期從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Publisher"
msgstr "複製出版商"

msgid "Copy Publisher from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將出版商從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Languages"
msgstr "複製語言"

msgid "Copy Languages from the source Epub to the Split Epub."
msgstr "將語言從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。"

msgid "Copy Source Title to Comments"
msgstr "複製源標題到簡介"

msgid "Copy Title from the source Epub to the Split Epub Comments."
msgstr "將標題從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub的簡介中。"

msgid "Link to Source book in Calibre in Comments"
msgstr "在書籍簡介中顯示源書籍在Calibre中的連結"

msgid "Include a Calibre link to the source Epub in the Split Epub Comments."
msgstr "在拆分後的書籍的簡介中包含源書籍在Calibre中的連結"

msgid "Link to Source URL Identifier in Comments"
msgstr "在書籍簡介中包含源書籍的識別符號的連結"

msgid "Include a link to the source Epub's URL Identifier(if present) in the Split Epub Comments."
msgstr "在拆分後的書籍簡介中包含源書籍的識別符號的連結(如果有的話)"

msgid "Copy Comments"
msgstr "複製簡介"

msgid "Copy Comments from the source Epub to the Split Epub.  Adds \"Split from:\" to the comments."
msgstr "將簡介從源Epub複製到拆分的Epub。 新增 \"拆分自:\"到簡介中. "

msgid "These controls aren't plugin settings as such, but convenience buttons for setting Keyboard shortcuts and getting all the EpubSplit confirmation dialogs back again."
msgstr "下述設定本身不屬於外掛設定，而是用於設定鍵盤快捷鍵和再次返回所有 Epub拆分 確認對話方塊的快捷按鈕。"

msgid "Keyboard shortcuts..."
msgstr "快捷鍵..."

msgid "Edit the keyboard shortcuts associated with this plugin"
msgstr "編輯與此外掛關聯的鍵盤快捷鍵"

msgid "Reset disabled &confirmation dialogs"
msgstr "重置禁用的確認對話方塊（&C）"

msgid "Reset all show me again dialogs for the EpubSplit plugin"
msgstr "重置 Epub拆分 外掛的所有“再次顯示”對話方塊"

msgid "View library preferences..."
msgstr "檢視書庫首選項..."

msgid "View data stored in the library database for this plugin"
msgstr "檢視儲存在書庫資料庫中的此外掛的資料"

msgid "Done"
msgstr "完成"

msgid "Confirmation dialogs have all been reset"
msgstr "確認對話方塊已全部重置"

msgid "Save Source column:"
msgstr "保留原欄目"

msgid "If set, the column below will be populated with the template below to record the source of the split file."
msgstr "如果設定，下述欄目的內容將使用下述模板來填充，以記錄拆分的檔案的原始資訊。"

msgid "Choose a column to populate with template on split."
msgstr "選擇在拆分時要根據模板填充資料的欄目。"

msgid "Template from source book. Example: {title} by {authors}"
msgstr "根據源書籍建立的模板。例如: {title} 作者 {authors} "

msgid "If you have custom columns defined, they will be listed below.  Choose if you would like these columns copied to new split books."
msgstr "如果你有自定義欄目，他們將顯示在下面。選擇你希望複製到拆分後的新書中的欄目。"

msgid "Copy this %s column to new split books..."
msgstr "複製該 %s 欄目到拆分後的新書..."

msgid "Only one automatic Multiple Split mode can be active a time.  Select which and configure settings below."
msgstr "一次只能啟用一種自動拆分模式。選擇並配置下面的設定。"

msgid "The title for each new book will be taken from the first included section in the Table of Contents."
msgstr "每本新書的標題都將取自目錄中包含的第一個章節。"

msgid "Sections that do not have a Table of Contents entry will be included in the previous section."
msgstr "沒在目錄條目中的章節將包含在前一章節中。"

msgid "You may edit the Table of Contents entries before splitting."
msgstr "你可以在拆分前編輯目錄條目。"

msgid "Create a new book for each selected section."
msgstr "為每個選定的章節建立一本新書。"

msgid "Create new books every N selected sections."
msgstr "為選定的每N個章節建立一本新書。"

msgid "Number of Sections"
msgstr "章節數"

msgid "Sections per new book"
msgstr "每本新書的章節數"

msgid "If the last book would contain fewer than sections than the Orphan Limit, include them in the previous book instead.  Last book will have more than N sections when that happens."
msgstr "如果最後一本書包含的章節數少於“最小章節數”，則將其包含在上一本書中。發生這種情況時，最後一本書將包含 N個 以上的章節。"

msgid "Orphan Limit"
msgstr "最小章節數"

msgid "Limit for orphan sections"
msgstr "限制生成一本書時需要的最小章節數"

msgid "Create N new books, dividing the selected sections between them as evenly as possible."
msgstr "建立 N 本新書，儘可保證每本書的章節數接近。"

msgid "Note that 'evenly' means the number of sections with entries in the Table of Contents, not files or size by bytes or words."
msgstr "請注意，“接近”指包含的目錄中的章節數，而不是檔案數或位元組數或字數。"

msgid "Number of books"
msgstr "書籍數"

msgid "Split all selected sections into this many new books, dividing the sections evenly between them."
msgstr "將選定的章節拆分成這麼多本新書，並儘量保證章節數接近。"

msgid "<p><b><i>Double click to copy from sample.</i></b></p>"
msgstr "<p><b><i>雙擊從樣本複製。</i></b></p>"

msgid "Search for string in Table of Contents Entries."
msgstr "在目錄條目中搜尋字串。"

msgid "Find:"
msgstr "搜尋:"

msgid "Find"
msgstr "搜尋"

msgid "Choose how found entries will be treated."
msgstr "選擇如何處理找到的條目。"

msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "區分大小寫"

msgid "Search for case sensitive string; don't treat Harry, HARRY and harry all the same."
msgstr "區分大小寫地搜尋字串；不要將 \"Harry\"、\"HARRY\" 和 \"harry\" 視為相同。"

msgid "Configure"
msgstr "配置"

msgid "Configure Plugin"
msgstr "設定外掛"

msgid "New Book"
msgstr "新書"

msgid "Make <i>one</i> new book containing the sections selected above and then edit its Metadata."
msgstr "製作<i>一本</i>包含上述選定部分的新書，然後編輯其後設資料。"

msgid "Get Size"
msgstr "獲取大小"

msgid "Calculate the size of the new book from the currently selected sections."
msgstr "根據當前選定的章節計算新書的大小。"

msgid "Highlight"
msgstr "高亮"

msgid "Select"
msgstr "選中"

msgid "Check"
msgstr ""

msgid "Missing Title(s)"
msgstr "缺失標題"

msgid "Some selected sections don't have a Table of Contents text."
msgstr "部分選定的章節沒有對應的目錄條目。"

msgid "If you continue, those sections will be included with the last prior section that did have a Table of Contents text."
msgstr "如果繼續，這些部分將包括在上一節中，該節具有目錄文字。"

msgid "If you cancel, you can go back and add Table of Contents entries."
msgstr "如果取消，您將返回並可新增目錄條目。"

msgid "Double click to edit the Table of Contents entry for a section."
msgstr "雙擊以編輯章節對應的目錄條目。"

msgid "Guide"
msgstr "型別"

msgid "HREF"
msgstr "源內容"

msgid "Table of Contents"
msgstr "目錄項"

msgid "Use Context Menu (right-click) on selected sections to check or uncheck all selected sections."
msgstr "在所選部分上使用上下文選單（右鍵單擊）來勾選或取消勾選所有所選部分。"

msgid "Indicates 'special' pages: copyright, titlepage, etc."
msgstr "表示“特殊”頁面：版權、標題頁等"

msgid "Click and copy hotkey to copy text.\nDouble-click to edit ToC entry.\nPipes(|) divide different ToC entries to the same place."
msgstr "單擊並複製熱鍵以複製文字。\n單擊可編輯目錄條目。\n管道（|）將不同的目錄條目劃分到同一位置。"

msgid "Section Sample"
msgstr "章節示例"

msgid "Check Selected"
msgstr "選擇所選項"

msgid "Uncheck Selected"
msgstr "不選所選項"

msgid "Splitting Sections..."
msgstr "分拆章節中..."

msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

msgid " - %s estimated until done"
msgstr " - %s 預計直至完成"

msgid "%d day"
msgstr "%d 天"

msgid "%d days"
msgstr "%d 天"

msgid "%d hour"
msgstr "%d 小時"

msgid "%d hours"
msgstr "%d 小時"

msgid "%d minute"
msgstr "%d 分鐘"

msgid "%d minutes"
msgstr "%d 分鐘"

msgid "%d second"
msgstr "%d 秒"

msgid "%d seconds"
msgstr "%d 秒"

msgid "less than 1 second"
msgstr "少於1秒"

msgid "EpubSplit"
msgstr "Epub拆分"

msgid "Split off part of an EPUB into a new book."
msgstr "將epub的拆分為新書"

msgid "Select One Book"
msgstr "選取一本書"

msgid "Please select exactly one book to split."
msgstr "請只選擇一本書"

msgid "EPUB3 Detected"
msgstr "檔案為EPUB3格式"

msgid "This plugin only works on EPUB2 format ebooks."
msgstr "該外掛僅用於EPUB2格式的電子書."

msgid "No EPUB"
msgstr "無EPUB"

msgid "This plugin only works on EPUB format ebooks."
msgstr "該外掛僅用於EPUB格式的電子書."

msgid "Select Sections to Split Off"
msgstr "選擇需拆分的章節"

msgid "No Sections Selected"
msgstr "未選擇章節"

msgid "Book(s) not split.\n\nYou must select at least one section to split."
msgstr "書籍未拆分.\n\n你至少需選擇一本用於拆分的書."

msgid "New Books Created"
msgstr "新書籍已建立"

msgid "%s New Books Created."
msgstr "%s 本新書已建立."

msgid "Computing size of EPUB..."
msgstr "正在計算EPUB的大小..."

msgid "Finished computing size of EPUB."
msgstr "完成計算EPUB的大小。"

msgid "Size of New Book"
msgstr "新書的大小"

msgid "New EPUB File Size:"
msgstr "新EPUB檔案大小:"

msgid "%s Split"
msgstr "%s 分拆"

msgid "Calibre Library Link"
msgstr "Calibre 書庫連結"

msgid "Source URL"
msgstr "源URL"

msgid "Split from:"
msgstr "分拆自:"

msgid "You can enable or disable Edit Metadata in Preferences > Plugins > EpubSplit."
msgstr "你可以在首選項 >外掛 > Epub拆分 啟用或禁用後設資料編輯 ."

msgid "The book for the new Split EPUB has been created and default metadata filled in.\n\nHowever, the EPUB will *not* be created until after you've reviewed, edited, and closed the metadata dialog that follows.\n\nYou can fill in the metadata yourself, or use download metadata for known books.\n\nIf you download or add a cover image, it will be included in the generated EPUB."
msgstr "新Split EPub的書籍已經建立，並填寫了預設後設資料。\n\n然而，在您檢視、編輯和關閉隨後的後設資料對話方塊之前，才會 ** 建立EPub。\n\n您可以自己填寫後設資料，也可以使用已知書籍的下載後設資料。\n\n如果您下載或新增封面影象，它將包含在生成的EPub中。"

msgid "Splitting off from EPUB..."
msgstr "拆分自EPUB..."

msgid "Finished splitting off EPUB."
msgstr "完成EPUB拆分"

msgid "<b><u>%s</u> by %s</b> has been created and default metadata filled in."
msgstr "<b><u>%s</u> 作者 %s</b> 已建立並生成了預設後設資料."

msgid "EpubSplit now skips the Edit Metadata step by default."
msgstr "Epub拆分 現在預設跳過“編輯後設資料”步驟。"

msgid "Restart calibre now"
msgstr "現在重新啟動 calibre"
